import React from 'react'; import '../../resources/templates.css' function Template4() { const user= JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem("shaikhresume-user")); return (

{user.firstName.toUpperCase()} {user.lastName.toUpperCase()}

{user.Email}

{user.mobilenum}

{user.address}

Objective

{user.objective}

Education

{user.Education.map((Education) => (
{Education.year}:

{Education.Qualification} with {Education.Percentage}% in {Education.Institution}

))}

Experience

{user.Experience.map((exp) => (
{exp.year}:

{exp.Company} in {exp.Place}

))}

Projects

{user.projects.map((project) => (
{project.Title} [{project.year}]:

{project.description}

))}

Skills

{user.skills.map((skill) => ( {skill.technology} ))}
); } export default Template4;
